---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Open-source notices"><p class="eyebrow">Licenses</p><h1 class="text-4xl font-black">Open-source notices</h1><section class="panel prose-readable mt-8"><h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Vercel AI Elements</h2><p>Conversation, Message, and Tool patterns are adapted from Vercel AI Elements at commit <code>0c1f5e8c75273f0e95c8faa031544a8aa2bb1a5b</code>, Apache-2.0. Local modifications remove shadcn/runtime dependencies, support static evaluation events, and add accessibility labels.</p><h2 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">@pierre/diffs</h2><p>Candidate patches use the official React <code>PatchDiff</code> renderer from <code>@pierre/diffs@1.2.12</code>, Apache-2.0.</p><p class="mt-6">Full notices are maintained in <code>web/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md</code>.</p></section></BaseLayout>
